sentence: which states border states through which the mississippi traverses ?
sentence-with-vars: which states border states through which the state0 traverses ?
sql: select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' mississippi ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select border_info.border from border_info where border_info.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' state0 ' ) ;
